Name: objoid
column6: the oid of the object this security label pertains to

Name: classoid
column6: the oid of the system catalog this object appears in

Name: objsubid
column6: for a security label on a table column, this is the column number (the objoid and classoid refer to the table itself). for all other object types, this column is zero.

Name: provider
column6: the label provider associated with this label.

Name: label
column6: the security label applied to this object.
